ernment%20took%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoco%20pilots%2C%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20said%2C%20are%20important%20members%20of%20the%20railway%20family.%20%26quot%3BSince%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20misinformation%20and%20theatrics%20by%20opposition%20to%20demotivate%20our%20Loco%20pilots%2C%20let%20me%20make%20things%20very%20clear.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELoco%20pilots%20are%20important%20members%20of%20the%20railway%20family.%20Since%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20misinformation%20and%20theatrics%20by%20opposition%20to%20demotivate%20our%20Loco%20pilots%2C%20let%20me%20make%20things%20very%20clear%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnImproved%20working%20conditions%3B%3Cbr%3E%5CnDuty%20hours%20of%20loco%20pilots%20are%20carefully%20monitored.%20Rest%20is%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20(%40AshwiniVaishnaw)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAshwiniVaishnaw%2Fstatus%2F1810926844163793371%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuty%20hours%20of%20loco%20pilots%20are%20carefully%20monitored.%20Rest%20is%20provided%20meticulously%20after%20trips.%20The%20average%20duty%20hours%20are%20maintained%20within%20prescribed%20hours.%20The%20average%20is%20less%20than%208%20hours%20in%20the%20month%20of%20June%20this%20year.%20Only%20under%20exigencies%2C%20the%20trip%20duration%20exceeds%20the%20prescribed%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELoco%20cabs%2C%20from%20where%20pilots%20operate%20trains%2C%20were%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20bad%20shape%26quot%3B%20before%202014%2C%20the%20minister%20said.%20%26quot%3BSince%202014%2C%20cabs%20have%20been%20improved%20with%20ergonomic%20seats%2C%20and%20more%20than%207%2C000%20loco%20cabs%20are%20air-conditioned.%20New%20locomotives%20are%20manufactured%20with%20AC%20cabs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20underlining%20the%20change%20under%20the%20BJP-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20then%20proceeded%20to%20focus%20on%20how%20off-duty%20resting%20facilities%20for%20loco%20pilot%20had%20changed%20after%202014.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWhen%20pilots%20complete%20a%20trip%2C%20they%20come%20to%20running%20room%20for%20rest%20if%20they%20are%20out%20of%20headquarters.%20Before%202014%2C%20running%20rooms%20were%20in%20very%20bad%20shape.%20Almost%20all%20(558)%20running%20rooms%20are%20now%20air%20conditioned.%20In%20many%20running%20rooms%2C%20foot%20massagers%20are%20also%20provided.%20Incidentally%2C%20this%20was%20criticised%20by%20Congress%20without%20understanding%20the%20working%20conditions%20of%20loco%20pilots%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20the%20subject%20of%20recruitment%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2034%2C000%20running%20staff%20have%20been%20recruited%20and%20the%20process%20is%20on%20for%20getting%2018%2C000%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20attempt%20to%20demoralise%20railway%20family%20with%20fake%20news%20will%20fail.%20The%20entire%20rail%20parivar%20is%20united%20in%20serving%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railways%20minister's%20rebuttal%20comes%20days%20after%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Congress%20MP%20and%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20said%20that%20he%20met%20a%20section%20of%20loco%20pilots%20at%20New%20Delhi%20station%20and%20they%20complained%20of%20%26quot%3Blong%20working%20hours%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Binadequate%20facilities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lives%20of%20loco%20pilot%20had%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20derailed%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLoco%20pilots%20are%20compelled%20to%20work%2016%20hours%20a%20day%20in%20simmering%20cabins.%20There%20is%20no%20limit%20to%20work%20hours%2C%20no%20leave%20and%20not%20even%20basic%20facilities%20like%20urinals.%20They%20are%20breaking%20physically%20and%20mentally%20and%20getting%20sick.%20Making%20them%20run%20trains%20under%20such%20conditions%20is%20putting%20them%20and%20passengers'%20lives%20in%20danger%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%20will%20raise%20this%20issue%20in%20Parliament.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20also%20posted%20a%20video%20of%20his%20chat%20with%20loco%20pilots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20post%2C%20the%20Railways%20had%20said%20the%20loco%20pilots%20Mr%20Gandhi%20met%20were%20not%20from%20the%20Delhi%20division%20but%20were%20brought%20from%20outside.%20This%20was%2C%20however%2C%20countered%20by%20several%20loco%20pilots'%20associations%20who%20stressed%20that%20it%20was%20pointless%20to%20focus%20on%20divisions%20and%20zones%20as%20long%20as%20the%20pilots%20have%20similar%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi's%20meeting%20with%20loco%20pilots%20and%20the%20Railways%20minister's%20rebuttal%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20offensive%20against%20the%20Centre%20over%20railway%20accidents.%20The%20Congress%20government%20has%20been%20demanding%20Mr%20Vaishnaw's%20resignation%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20crash%20last%20month%20that%20left%2010%20people%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720607040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F2do98koo_rahul-gandhi-ashwini-vaishnaw_625x300_10_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fashwini-vaishnaw-rahul-gandhi-attempt-to-demoralise-railways-minister-rebuts-rahul-gandhi-on-loco-pilots-6075034%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Countering%20Congress's%20offensive%20on%20the%20work%20conditions%20of%20loco%20pilots%2C%20Railways%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20today%20accused%20the%20Opposition%20of%20trying%20to%20demoralise%20the%20Railway%20family%20with%20fake%20news.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonical