%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-seekers-careers-interviews-assessments-hiring-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eless-than-ideal%20picture%20for%20job%20searchers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20a%20service%20economy%2C%20and%20the%20service%20sector%20seems%20now%20to%20be%20struggling%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20rolling%20recession%20that%20hit%20interest%20rate-sensitive%20sectors%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20Julia%20Pollak%2C%20chief%20economist%20at%20ZipRecruiter%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20first%20saw%20tech%20and%20housing%2C%20real%20estate%20industries%20like%20that%20cool%20down%2C%20but%20we're%20now%20seeing%20weakness%20spill%20over%20into%20services%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20main%20engine%20of%20job%20growth%20in%20the%20US%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FoXgoz%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Month-over-month%20employment%20changes%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22452%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20a%20long%20time%20for%20the%20leisure%20and%20hospitality%20industry%20to%20get%20back%20to%20where%20employment%20was%20in%20February%202020%3B%20it%20only%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esurpassed%20this%20level%20this%20past%20May%2C%20while%20the%20economy%20as%20a%20whole%20passed%20that%20benchmark%20in%20June%202022.%20Still%2C%20the%20industry%20largely%20saw%20strong%20monthly%20job%20gains%20following%20the%20losses%20it%20faced%20early%20on%20in%20the%20pandemic%2C%20averaging%20205%2C000%20jobs%20a%20month%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20breakneck%20pace%20has%20slowed%20to%20a%20trickle.%20Data%20out%20Friday%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Fces%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBureau%20o