0door%3A%20their%20bottom%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20annual%20spending%20on%20shipping%20has%20ballooned%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20particularly%20as%20it%20ramped%20up%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-one-day-shipping-promise-snag-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone-day%20and%20same-day%20shipping%3C%2Fa%3E%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20spent%20%2489.5%20billion%20on%20shipping%20in%202023%20%E2%80%94%20an%20increase%20of%20roughly%207%25%20over%202022%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fd18rn0p25nwr6d.cloudfront.net%2FCIK-0001018724%2Fc7c14359-36fa-40c3-b3ca-5bf7f3fa0b96.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannual%20filing%20with%20the%20SEC.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20despite%20offering%20options%20like%20%26quot%3BAmazon%20Day%20Delivery%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20customers%20can%20choose%20to%20wait%20a%20few%20days%20if%20the%20order%20isn't%20urgent%2C%20and%20Amazon%20will%20try%20to%20put%20as%20many%20items%20in%20the%20same%20box%20as%20it%20can.%20(Amazon%20sometimes%20offers%20credits%20to%20customers%20who%20choose%20this%20option.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelivering%20orders%20to%20a%20single%20pick-up%20point%20instead%20of%20going%20out%20on%20an%20hours-long%20route%20through%20suburbia%20saves%20time%20%E2%80%94%20and%20probably%20gas%20%E2%80%94%20compared%20with%20individual%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20shipping%20back%20items%20that%20customers%20want%20to%20return%20is%20also%20steep%20for%20Amazon%20and%20other%20retailers%20%E2%80%94%20so%20steep%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-walmart-and-target-let-customers-keep-some-returns-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20may%20give%20you%20a%20refund%20and%20tell%20you%20to%20keep%20the%20product.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20that%20has%20pushed%20Amazon%20to%20come%20up%20wit