Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20boss%20joined%20the%20call%20and%20told%20me%20the%20news%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-google-juggled-jobs-trader-joes-careers-corporate-life-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20was%20being%20laid%20off%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20shocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20held%20it%20together%20during%20the%20call%2C%20but%20I%20was%20absolutely%20devastated.%20It%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20being%20broken%20up%20with%20over%20text.%20In%20the%20back%20of%20my%20head%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20I%20had%20just%20paid%20my%20security%20deposit%20on%20a%20new%20rental%20and%20I%20didn't%20know%20if%20I%20was%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20pay%20next%20month's%20rent.%20The%20safety%20that%20I%20had%20worked%20to%20create%20for%20my%20son%20had%20gone%20out%20the%20window%20all%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20gave%20me%20a%20severance%20package%20which%20I%20used%20to%20pay%20a%20month%20of%20rent%20and%20pay%20my%20car%20off.%20The%20lump%20sum%20was%20helpful%2C%20but%20as%20a%20single%20mother%2C%20I%20still%20needed%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20whatever%20unexpected%20costs%20came%20next.%20Wasting%20time%20was%20not%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba2166c4-f1c2-40a8-91eb-7071e3e91b5d%5C%22%3EMy%20lay-off%20was%20difficult%2C%20but%20it%20ended%20up%20being%20a%20blessing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20I%20jumped%20back%20into%20the%20job%20hunt.%20I%20posted%20about%20my%20layoff%20to%20my%20LinkedIn%20network%20and%20even%20made%20TikTok%20videos%20about%20my%20experience.%20I%20applied%20endlessly%20to%20jobs%20on%20LinkedIn%20and%20Indeed%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghost-jobs-why-some-companies-dont-respond-to-applications-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egot%20ghosted%20by%20several%20recruiters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20overcome%20with%20worry%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20push%20through%20for