chchh%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20sought%20the%20Gujarat%20government's%20reply%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20goes%20back%20to%202005%20when%20the%20108%20hectares%20was%20allotted%20to%20Adani%20Ports.%20In%202010%2C%20when%20Adani%20Ports%20%26amp%3B%20SEZ%20started%20fencing%20the%20land%2C%20residents%20of%20Navinal%20village%20there%20approached%20the%20high%20court%20with%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20and%20challenged%20the%20allotment%20of%20231%20hectares%20of%20grazing%20land%20to%20Adani%20Ports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20argued%20that%20the%20village%20was%20facing%20a%20shortage%20of%20grazing%20land%20and%20this%20allotment%20would%20leave%20them%20with%20only%2045%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20court%20disposed%20of%20the%20matter%20after%20the%20state%20government%20said%20that%20an%20order%20granting%20387%20hectares%20of%20government%20land%20for%20grazing%20had%20been%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20that%20did%20not%20happen%2C%20a%20contempt%20petition%20was%20filed.%20In%202015%2C%20the%20state%20government%20filed%20a%20review%20petition%20and%20told%20the%20court%20that%20only%2017%20hectares%20are%20available%20to%20be%20allocated%20to%20the%20village%20panchayat.%20The%20state%20government%20proposed%20that%20it%20may%20allocate%20the%20remaining%20land%20about%207%20kilometres%20away.%20The%20villagers%20rejected%20this%2C%20contending%20that%20it's%20too%20far%20for%20cattle%20to%20graze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20this%20year%2C%20the%20court%20asked%20a%20senior%20revenue%20official%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20solution.%20The%20official%20responded%20that%20the%20state%20government%20had%20decided%20to%20take%20back%20nearly%20108%20hectares%20--%20266%20acres%20--%20of%20land%20that%20had%20been%20allocated%20to%20Adani%20Ports%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revenue%20department%20said%20the%20state%20will%20%26quot%3Breplenish%2