otebook.%20But%20a%20science%20fair%20at%20the%20end%20of%20term%20had%20him%20revisit%20this%20doodle.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20supposed%20to%20come%20up%20with%20something%20innovative%20and%20I%20thought%20of%20going%20back%20to%20this%20idea.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20Meditel%20took%20shape%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20stretch%20to%20say%20that%20the%20innovation%20has%20grown%20with%20Nikhil%3B%20the%20two%20have%20shared%20a%20parallel%20journey%2C%20as%20the%20idea%20transcended%20from%20being%20a%20PowerPoint%20presentation%20to%20a%20paper%20model%20to%20a%20basic%20prototype.%20From%20there%20it%20transformed%20into%20a%20full-blown%20electrical%20model%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20nuances%20Nikhil%20found%20himself%20explaining%20to%20none%20other%20than%20football%20legend%20David%20Beckham%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trajectory%20has%20been%20dream-like.%20And%20in%20a%20tete-a-tete%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Nikhil%20lets%20us%20in%20on%20the%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20first%20Meditel%20model%20that%20Nikhil%20built%20when%20he%20was%20in%20Class%207%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-09-at-11.48.13-AM-1720526791-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupl