-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fromeeta2-1720183125-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fromeeta2-1720183125-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fromeeta2-1720183125-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERomeeta%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20female%20Electro%20Technical%20Officer%20(ETO)%20on%20a%20Maersk%20ship%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERomeeta%20recalls%20her%20first%20experience%20on%20a%20ship%20at%20Maersk.%20Her%20first%20contract%20was%20for%20four%20months%20and%20began%20from%20Singapore%20on%20a%20merchant%20vessel%20with%2020%20men.%20As%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20she%20received%20a%20cold%20welcome%20even%20before%20she%20could%20place%20her%20suitcase%20in%20her%20cabin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20manager%20had%20never%20seen%20a%20woman%20in%20this%20role.%20He%20was%20really%20dominating%20and%20kept%20telling%20me%20that%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20do%20this%20job.%20It%20was%20extremely%20demotivating.%20Imagine%20listening%20to%20this%20all%20the%20time!%20I%20survived%20the%20four%20months%20and%20proved%20him%20wrong%20through%20my%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20ETO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20proudly%20shares%20that%20at%20the%20end%20of%20her%20first%20contract%2C%20the%20same%20manager%20who%20had%20initially%20judged%20her%20conducted%20her%20appraisal.%20He%20gave%20her%20a%20good%20recommendation%20and%20told%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20wrong%20to%20judge%20you%20without%20seeing%20your%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20interviewed%20Romeeta%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20ponder%20how%20water%20has%20no%20ceiling%2C%20but%20even%20there%2C%20men%20have%20built%20a%20glass%20ceiling%2C%20which%20she%20successfully%20broke.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20gave%20you%20the%2