rsonally%2C%20the%20journey%20from%20being%20a%20designer%20to%20an%20innovator%20has%20been%20extremely%20fulfilling%20for%20me.%20I%20always%20strived%20to%20do%20impact-driven%20work%20and%20received%20many%20awards%20and%20recognition%20for%20it.%20We%20are%20working%20at%20a%20small%20level%20but%20wish%20to%20expand%20this%20pan%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMore%20than%20anything%2C%20we%20require%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20support%20to%20further%20our%20work%20to%20establish%20a%20sustainable%20recycling%20model%2C%20which%20will%20help%20us%20divert%20this%20waste%20at%20a%20large%20scale.%20If%20they%20can%20also%20fund%20training%20programmes%20for%20women%20workers%20and%20design%20policies%20that%20ensure%20the%20waste%20is%20not%20thrown%20in%20water%20bodies%20or%20landfills%2C%20that%20will%20help%20us%20further%20the%20cause%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Golden%20Feathers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720017502000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgolden-feathers-1-1718797523.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355399%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Radhesh%20Agrahari%20runs%20Golden%20Feathers%2C%20a%20startup%20which%20converts%20chicken%20butchery%20waste%20including%20feathers%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98wool-like%E2%80%99%20fibre%20and%20handmade%20paper.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355399%2Fstartup-converting-chicken-butchery-waste-into-wool-shawls-jackets-paper-manure-golden-feather-radhesh-agrahari%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20CSR%20Initiative%20Works%20For%20Equal%20Education%2C%20Helps%20Kids%20of%20Construction%20Workers%20Join%20Schools%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis