%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938-768x511.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355394%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221006%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMeru%20International%20School%20has%20launched%20a%20daycare%20centre%20called%20Meru%20Aveksha.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20shared%20this%20with%20Ramu%20Rao%20Jupally%2C%20the%20vice%20chairman%20of%20My%20Home%20Constructions%2C%20Ramu%20Rao%20immediately%20agreed%20to%20help%2C%20and%20the%20team%20reached%20out%20to%20Meghana%20Gorukanti%C2%A0%20Jupally%2C%20who%20runs%20Meru%20International%20School%2C%20to%20find%20a%20solution.%20How%20could%20they%20provide%20early%20childhood%20education%20in%20a%20nurturing%20and%20safe%20environment%3F%20By%20building%20a%20daycare%20centre-cum-play%20school%20called%20the%20Meru%20Aveksha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20Meru%20Aveksha%20centre%20was%20opened%20last%20year%20at%20an%20upcoming%20residential%20project%20by%20the%20My%20Home%20Group%20in%20Kokapet%2C%20Hyderabad.%20Over%20the%20past%2012%20months%2C%20two%20more%20centres%20were%20opened%20in%20the%20city.%20The%20three%20centres%20cater%20to%20over%20150%20children%2C%20from%20infants%20to%2012-year-olds%2C%20providing%20them%20a%20safe%20place%20to%20stay%20during%20the%20day%2C%20while%20empowering%20them%20with%20the%20necessary%20skill%20sets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESafety%2C%20education%20and%20food%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meru%20Aveksha%20team%20first%20spoke%20to%20the%20parents%20and%20children%20of%20the%20migrant%20labourers%20to%20understand%20the%20major%20gaps.%20They%20found%20that%20there%20was%20no%20facility%20for%20these%20children%20to%20spend%20time%20during%20the%20day%20and%20they%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20gain%20admission%20in%20government%20schools%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20basic%20identification%20documents%20like%20an%20Aadhar%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20at%20Meru%20Aveksha%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022-300x202.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022-500x336.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022-768x517.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-28-at-10.37.29-AM-1720006022-150x101.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355396%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22861%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChildren%20at%20Meru%20Aveksha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20these%20children%20would%20either%20come%20to%20the%20site%20with%20their%20parents%20or%20stay%20at%20home.%20Some%20of%20the%20older%20children%20sometimes%20also%20start%20working%20very%20early.%20We%20wanted%20to%20provide%20them%20safety%2C%20education%20and%20food.%20We%20found%20that%20the%20best%20way%20to%20do%20this%20would%20be%20through%20a%20daycare%20and%20playschool%20centre%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Meghana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilt%20at%20construction%20sites%2C%20these%20centres%20are%20spread%20over%20half%20an%20acre.%20They%20have%20an%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20play%20area%2C%20classrooms%2C%20audio-visual%20rooms%20and%20much%20more.%20Teachers%20from%20Meru%20International%20School%20built%20a%20basic%20to%20advanced%20curriculum%20that%20would%20focus%20on%20languages%2C%20numeracy%2C%20physical%20activity%2C%20arts%20and%20crafts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20health%20and%20hygiene%20skills%2C%20depending%20upon%20the%20age%20of%20the%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpen%20from%208%3A30%20am%20to%203%3A30%20pm%2C%20each%20day%20starts%20with%20circle%20time%2C%20indoor%20playtime%2C%20toilet%20breaks%20(to%20inculcate%20good%20habits)%2C%20English%2C%20Hindi%2C%20and%20Math%20classes%2C%20along%20with%20audio-visual%20aids%20(music%2Fdance%2Fmovies%2Fstorytelling%2Fart)%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20challenge%20was%20convincing%20the%20parents.%20Only%20after%20the%20parents%20accompanied%20the%20children%20to%20the%20centre%20daily%20did%20they%20understand%20the%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20counsel%20the%20parents%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20early%20education.%20Our%20idea%20is%20to%20create%20a%20habit%20of%20coming%20to%20a%20structured%20space%20daily.%20After%20attending%20this%20centre%20for%20two%20or%20three%20years%2C%20they%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20join%20a%20mainstream%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Meghana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20many%20interventions%20which%20impressed%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20education%2C%20children%20started%20attending%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20basics%20of%20early%20childhood%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20centre%20has%20a%20caretaker%20and%20two%20qualified%20staff%20members.%20The%20curriculum%20is%20designed%20to%20improve%20learning%20outcomes%20and%20bridge%20the%20gaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20students%20first%20start%20with%20a%20common%20curriculum%2C%20which%20includes%20alphabets.%20Once%20they%20progress%2C%20they%20are%20given%20textbooks%20and%20worksheets%20for%20the%20next%20level.%20They%20are%20then%20divided%20into%20smaller%20cohorts%20and%20taught%20as%20per%20their%20levels%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Meghana%2C%20adding%20that%20each%20student%20is%20provided%20with%20a%20uniform%2C%20textbooks%20and%20worksheets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-14-1720014160.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Features%20of%20the%20curriculum%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-14-1720014160.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-14-1720014160-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-14-1720014160-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-14-1720014160-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-14-1720014160-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355457%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20change%20that%20the%20Meru%20Aveksha%20centre%20members%20have%20noticed%20in%20the%20children%20is%20a%20behavioural%20change.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20attitude%20towards%20themselves%20has%20changed.%20From%20not%20attending%20classes%20post-lunch%2C%20they%20all%20come%20back%20now.%20They%20have%20started%20enjoying%20themselves.%20The%20most%20critical%20change%20we%20have%20seen%20is%20that%20they%20are%20engaged%20and%20interested%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Meghana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20their%20learning%20levels%20and%20understanding%2C%20their%20socio-emotional%20skills%20have%20developed%20to%20a%20great%20extent%2C%20according%20to%20her.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20catering%20to%20a%20segment%20that%20is%20completely%20neglected.%20They%20are%20learning%20for%20about%20two%20hours%20a%20day%20in%20a%20safe%20environment%20which%20is%20the%20biggest%20impact%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meru%20Aveshka%20team%20wants%20to%20share%20this%20model%20with%20other%20real%20estate%20developers%20so%20that%20all%20construction%20sites%20can%20start%20a%20daycare%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20are%20interested%20in%20learning%20more%20about%20this%20model%2C%20you%20can%20email%20them%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ameruaveksha%40meruinternationalschool.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emeruaveksha%40meruinternationalschool.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20prevent%20children%20being%20left%20alone%20at%20home.%20Every%20child%20deserves%20a%20good%20education%20and%20a%20chance%20at%20a%20better%20life.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20give%20them%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Meghana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720016654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meghana%20Gorukanti%20Jupally%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Meru%20International%20School%20has%20launched%20a%20daycare%20centre%20called%20Meru%20Aveksha%2C%20which%20helps%20integrate%20kids%20of%20migrant%20workers%20into%20mainstream%20education.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%2