2C%20straw%20and%20wood%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289271%2Fkerala-couple-build-zero-cement-eco-friendly-home-with-recycled-material-around-natural-rocks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusing%20zero%20cement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20journey%20back%20to%20his%20childhood%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20on%20a%20farm%2C%20Mustafa%20always%20missed%20living%20in%20the%20lush%2C%20green%20area.%20The%20inspiration%20behind%20the%20project%20was%20partly%20because%20he%20wanted%20to%20relive%20his%20childhood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20development%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Kerala%2C%20he%20felt%20like%20the%20green%20cover%20was%20reducing%20massively.%20In%20a%20bid%20to%20do%20his%20part%20in%20bringing%20it%20back%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20undertake%20the%20project.%20It%20was%20a%20friend%20who%20alerted%20him%20of%20the%20land%20where%20Greenara%20now%20stands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mustafa%20PA%2C%20founder%20of%20Greenara%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fe