her%20story%20is%2C%20I%20am%20intrigued%20by%20what%E2%80%99s%20behind%20her.%20Shruthi%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20of%20the%20eco-friendly%20decor%20she%20has%20created%20through%20her%20brand%20%E2%80%98Ombak%E2%80%99%20proves%20to%20be%20an%20apt%20description%20as%20my%20gaze%20follows%20the%20pieces%20set%20in%20the%20backdrop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20beauty%20equals%20%E2%80%94%20if%20not%20surpasses%20%E2%80%94%20mainstream%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295373%2Feconiture-turns-plastic-waste-into-sustainable-furniture-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edecor%20alternatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20often%20manufactured%20using%20plastic%2C%20finished%20wood%20and%20treated%20fabrics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20%E2%80%98Ombak%E2%80%99%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98a%20large%20wave%E2%80%99%20in%20Bahasa%20(the%20language%20spoken%20in%20Indonesia)%2C%20Shruthi%20wants%20to%20urge%20consumers%20to%20invite%20sustainability%20into%20their%20homes%20for%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%2C%20eventually%20making%20it%20a%20permanent%20fixture%20in%20their%20daily%20lifestyles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20from%20a%20management%20professional%20engaged%20in%20business%20development%20for%20five%20years%20to%20an%20entrepreneur%20has%20had%20its%20share%20of%20twists%20and%20turns.%20And%20there%20was%20one%20pivotal%20moment%20that%20marked%20the%20shift.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20oversee%20design%20and%20marketing%20for%20brands%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20space%20as%20part%20of%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20advertising%20business.%20I%20would%20often%20be%20tasked%20with%20designing%20the%20stalls%20at%20exhibitions%20where%20these%20brands%20would%20display%20some%20of%20their%20work.%20It%20was%20during%20these%20times%20that%20I%20began%20to%20get%20interested%20in%20home%20design%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20early%20on%2C%20Shruthi%20insists%20she%20saw%20furniture%20and%20home%20decor%20as%20a%20route%20that%20would%20enable%20her%20to%20champion%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F304140%2Fmba-graduate-turns-banana-stem-waste-into-natural-fibre-eco-friendly-handicraft-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20fibres%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CA%20means%20towards%20an%20end%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20work%20on%20Ombak%20began%20two%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20albeit%20unofficially%2C%20since%20the%20brand%20was%20just%20a%20project%20back%20then%20%E2%80%94%20things%20took%20off%20when%20Shruthi%20moved%20to%20Indonesia%20following%20her%20marriage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20provided%20her%20a%20window%20into%20a%20new%20culture%2C%20one%20that%20displayed%20great%20acceptance%20of%20eco-friendly%20decor%20and%20was%20setting%20a%20precedent%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20in%20this%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsustainable-furniture-1719584001.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ombak's%20range%20of%20products%20feature%20baskets%20made%20out%20of%20banana%20fibre%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsustainable-furniture-1719584001.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsustainable-furniture-1719584001-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsustainable-furniture-1719584001-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsustainable-furniture-1719584001-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.theb